            <text align="left">-------------------------------------------------------------------------</text>
        </line>
        <line>
            <text align="center" length="65">이용해 주셔서 감사합니다.</text>
        </line>
        <line>
            <text align="center" length="65">또 찾아주세요.</text>
        </line>
